{
  "stem": "6736.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Our-- most of our time was spent being busy with-- you can imagine my mother had seven children.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I will never forget that the 1937 she had children every second year.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In 1937, she had no children.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So she said, God doesn't want me to have any more children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she did the cooking and the washing and the ironing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and we made plenty holes in the-- ripped our shirts and ripped our pants.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she did all that work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So she had no time for any other things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My father, after he finished the work, he would-- loved the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he mostly davened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And [NON-ENGLISH] 22 there was the rebbe from [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was called the [NON-ENGLISH] Rebbe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he was a composer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He composed a lot of new songs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And my father would know how to sing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He was not exactly a cantor, but like a-- a [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he would be-- when he-- the rebbe composed a new song, a new prayer, he would go over with his son, [NON-ENGLISH], and with my father.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So that's how he was busy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] Rebbe.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the Sabbath was observed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the street, there was not a single store open on the Sabbath.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, there was no problem.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in '37 and '38, refugees from Germany, Jewish people, were chased out and they would come to Krakow.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they will talk about the-- certain things that happened in Germany.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there was always an excuse that the Germans chasing out the Jews who came from Poland, who were not born in Germany.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That they took away jobs from the Germans or they cheat on the Germans.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all our politicking was done in the shul.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because, uh, we had no radios.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
